column1:
Sums may not equal to totals due to rounding.
1) Many states do not maintain records on publicly-owned  vehicles,. Total may not represent an accurate count of the total number of publicly-owned vehicles.
(2) Poor quality data; estimated by FHWA based on State reported data or data from secondary sources. 
(3) State did not provide data; estimated by FHWA based on prior year's data or data from secondary sources.
